 default file permission-->644
 default directory persmisson-->755
 umash default permisson -->0022
 full permission--777
 read+write ermisson-->666
 
 to give permission to the file 
 #chmod 777 filename
 to give write permissions
 #chmod +r filename
 to remove write permissios
 #chmod -r filenae
 
 to change directory and subdirectory permissions
 #chmod -R 777 filename
 
 to know the file on the time based
 #ls -lt 
 
 to see recursive order(desindeing order)
 #ls -ltr
 
 to copy one file into one directory
 #cp copyfilename directoryname/--->#cp soure destination/
 
 to copy one directory into anthoer
 #cp -rf source destination
